content: अप्रमेय {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Immeasurable, unbounded, boundless; °महिमा <ls>Mv. 4. 30.</ls> {@--2@} That which cannot be properly ascertained, understood &c.; inscrutable, unfathomable (of person or thing); अचिंत्यस्याप्रमेयस्य कार्यतत्त्वार्थवित्प्रभुः <ls>Ms. 1. 3</ls>; <ls n="Ms.">12. 94.</ls> {@--3@} Not to be proved or demonstrated (as Brahma). --यं Brahma.
